statements.sql: select `categories`.`id`, `categories`.`name`, `categories`.`slug`, (select `image` from `products` inner join `types` on `products`.`type_id` = `types`.`id` where `types`.`category_id` = `categories`.`id` order by `products`.`updated_at` desc limit 1) as `image`, (select MAX(products.updated_at) from `products` inner join `types` on `products`.`type_id` = `types`.`id` where `types`.`category_id` = `categories`.`id`) as `latest_update` from `categories` where exists (select 1 from `types` inner join `products` on `products`.`type_id` = `types`.`id` where `types`.`category_id` = `categories`.`id`) and `categories`.`deleted_at` is null group by `categories`.`id`, `categories`.`code`, `categories`.`name`, `categories`.`slug`, `categories`.`description` order by `latest_update` desc limit 5

select `products`.`id`, `products`.`code`, `products`.`title`, `products`.`slug`, `products`.`image`, IFNULL(SUM(oi.quantity), 0) as total_quantity, MAX(oi.updated_at) as last_update from `products` left join `order_items` as `oi` on `products`.`id` = `oi`.`product_id` where `products`.`deleted_at` is null group by `products`.`id`, `products`.`code`, `products`.`title`, `products`.`slug`, `products`.`image` order by `total_quantity` desc, `last_update` desc limit 4

select * from `categories` where exists (select * from `types` where `categories`.`id` = `types`.`category_id` and exists (select * from `products` where `types`.`id` = `products`.`type_id` and `products`.`deleted_at` is null) and `types`.`deleted_at` is null) and `categories`.`deleted_at` is null

select `categories`.`id`, `categories`.`name`, `categories`.`slug`, COALESCE(SUM(order_items.quantity), 0) as total_quantity from `categories` left join `types` on `categories`.`id` = `types`.`category_id` left join `products` on `types`.`id` = `products`.`type_id` left join `order_items` on `products`.`id` = `order_items`.`product_id` left join `orders` on `order_items`.`order_id` = `orders`.`id` and `orders`.`status` = 'Paid' where `categories`.`deleted_at` is null group by `categories`.`id`, `categories`.`name`, `categories`.`slug` order by `total_quantity` desc limit 5
select * from `social_media` where `name` is not null and `link` is not null and `social_media`.`deleted_at` is null
